        <h2>Preparing to hire Japan sales but funnel not yet defined?</h2>
        <p>Tell us where you are in the Japan GTM process. We'll identify what needs to be in place before a sales hire can succeed and what to build first.</p>
        <div class="article-cta__actions">
          <a href="/en/contact/" class="article-cta__btn article-cta__btn--primary">Contact Us</a>
